OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777050359
OL,3,CLiam Rosenior sacked as Chelsea head
OL,4,Ccoach following wretched run
OL,6,FLiam Rosenior has been sacked by
OL,7,FChelsea following a run of five
OL,8,Fconsecutive Premier League defeats in
OL,9,Fwhich the team failed to score.
OL,11,FThe former Hull and Strasbourg boss
OL,12,Fsigned a six-and-a-half-year deal in
OL,13,FJanuary and started brightly but the
OL,14,Fteam have plummeted down the table and
OL,15,Fare almost certain to miss out on
OL,16,Fqualification for the Champions League.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
