CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777050359
OL,3,CLiam Rosenior sacked as Chelsea head
OL,4,Ccoach following wretched run
OL,6,FThey were beaten comfortably 3-0 by
OL,7,FBrighton at the Amex Stadium on
OL,8,FTuesday, widely considered to have
OL,9,Fbeen the team's worst performance of
OL,10,Fthe season.
OL,12,FCalum McFarlane will take charge until
OL,13,Fthe end of the campaign, starting with
OL,14,FSunday's FA Cup semi-final against
OL,15,FLeeds.
OL,17,FA club statement read: "Chelsea
OL,18,FFootball Club has today parted company
OL,19,Fwith head coach Liam Rosenior.
OL,26,@yD@XOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
