CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777050359
OL,3,CLiam Rosenior sacked as Chelsea head
OL,4,Ccoach following wretched run
OL,6,F"On behalf of everyone at Chelsea FC,
OL,7,Fwe would like to place on record our
OL,8,Fgratitude to Liam and his staff for
OL,9,Fall their efforts during their time
OL,10,Fwith the club.
OL,12,F"Liam has always conducted himself
OL,13,Fwith the highest integrity and
OL,14,Fprofessionalism following his
OL,15,Fappointment midway through the season.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
